{"tid":1365384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 言語治療師聯署 促請政府積極回應及處理修例風波","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:21:20.000Z","uid":12856,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3345cad780e6e2f0614e902bb83a0a9df949bc93","tid":1365384,"uid":12856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"各位，我們是一群熱愛香港的言語治療師，想就香港最近發生的事表態。<br />\n <br />\n自《逃犯條例》修訂爭議開始，市民參與了數次大型遊行，當中的遊行人數達200萬，是歷年遊行之最。可惜政府沒有正面回應遊行所列的五大訴求之餘，對當中警察的濫權濫暴亦視而不見; 至最近2019年7月21日元朗港鐵站內發生了令人髮指的恐襲事件，政府亦沒有任何意圖為市民討回公道，亦不積極回應「成立獨立調查委員會」的訴求。<br />\n <br />\n我們就政府一手造成的政治問題表達最強烈的譴責。在此我們促請政府積極解決政治問題，並盡快正面回應五大訴求，秉公處理元朗恐襲事件，將有關暴徒繩之以法，修補日趨嚴重的社會撕裂。<br />\n <br />\n一群言語治療師上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/789617517781269/posts/2304273709648968?s=741973588&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F789617517781269%2Fposts%2F2304273709648968%3Fs%3D741973588%26sfns%3Dmo&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=0d119d04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/789617517781269/posts/2304273709648968?s=741973588&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nWe connected<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eac5391cb54fcca2daa80c2a5354e57761dbca","tid":1365384,"uid":12856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3ce1c0b08a27b59e52ef7700d8ac0d569086daf","tid":1365384,"uid":12856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比多啲行業嘅人睇到 遍地開花"},{"pid":"0da51a2177fe83f9823b154e4f1d6e6dda0707a9","tid":1365384,"uid":12856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gi